    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> Right now when you reload the page here what happens:\r\n\r\nI saw that it sometimes happen, sometimes not. I thought it would a problem but, it's rare that there is an input with a value, and even rarer when there are 2 searchbox and with two different way of initializing them. That's why I thought that it would not be interesting to put more complexity in order to fix this sub edge case given the odds. Happy to fix it further if it happens.",
